<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Return Request Received - Bamboo Shop</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background: #f6f9fc; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 40px auto; background: #fff; padding: 30px; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
    h2 { color: #2b7a0b; }
    table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 20px; }
    th, td { padding: 10px; text-align: left; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; }
    th { background-color: #f3f3f3; }
    a.button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 20px; background: #2b7a0b; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; margin-top: 20px; }
    a.button:hover { background: #25660a; }
    p { margin: 10px 0; }
    .next-steps { background: #f3f3f3; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin-top: 20px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Hello {{name}},</h2>
    <p>We have received your return request for <strong>Order #{{returnRequest.orderId}}</strong>. Our team will review it and update you shortly.</p>

    <h3>Return Items:</h3>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Product</th>
          <th>Reason</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        {{#each returnRequest.details}}
        <tr>
          <td>{{this.product.name}}</td>
          <td>{{this.reason}}</td>
        </tr>
        {{/each}}
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <p>Return Status: <strong>{{returnRequest.status}}</strong></p>

    <div class="next-steps">
      <h4>Next Steps:</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>Our team will review your return request within 3â€“5 business days.</li>
        <li>You will receive an email update once your return is approved or rejected.</li>
        <li>If approved, please follow the instructions to send the product back.</li>
        <li>Once we receive and inspect the returned item(s), the refund will be processed to your original payment method.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <p>Thank you for shopping with Bamboo Shop!</p>
    <p>Best regards,<br/>Bamboo Shop Team</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
